When attaching a screenshot, the dialog that pops up does not show the buttons at the bottom and entering "return" does not perform the highlighted action.

This is observed when viewing the browser windows on smaller screens, i.e., smaller resolutions. A workaround has been to zoom out or move across monitors where resolution available is higher, but it would be nice if the screen could auto-scale to support this such that visibility of the buttons is always available.

We understand that this is not a bug - just making a suggestion in case this is possible to address.
